Package <Unnamed>

Interface Summary
Cell An interface representing a Cell in Conway's Game of Life.
Game An interface for implementations of variants of Conway's Game of Life.
TwoDBoard An interface the defines how to use a board on Conway's Game of Life.
 

Class Summary
GameOfLife Problem Statement: Design three classes that will implement the provided interfaces to run Conway's Game of Life.
GameOfLifeBoard The GameOfLifeBoard class contains methods that directly control the state of cells in the board.
GameOfLifeCell This class implement the Cell class.
GameOfLifeGUI This is a generic GUI for use with running variations on Conway's Game of Life.
TwoDPanel The GameBoardCanvas class provides a canvas that will automatically draw and center a graphical board for a variant on Conway's Game of Life on an awt/swing component.
